---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import RelatedPosts from "../components/RelatedPosts.astro";

const metaTitle = "How to Maintain Your Swivel Seat";
const metaDescription =
  "Simple inspection, cleaning, lubrication, and storage tips to keep your Turnplus swivel seat reliable for years.";
const currentSlug = "how-to-maintain-your-swivel-seat";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.endsWith("/") ? import.meta.env.BASE_URL : `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/`;
const ogImage = `${base}logo.png`;
---

<BaseLayout title={metaTitle} description={metaDescription} headerVariant="solid">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta property="og:title" content={metaTitle} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={metaDescription} />
    <meta property="og:image" content={ogImage} />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content={metaTitle} />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content={metaDescription} />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content={ogImage} />
  </Fragment>

  <article class="article">
    <header class="article-head">
      <p class="article-date">June 19, 2023 · by vivek</p>
      <h1>How to Maintain Your Swivel Seat</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="article-grid">
      <div class="article-body">
        <p>
          The Turnplus swivel seat is a revolutionary product that makes it easier for people with disabilities to get in
          and out of their cars. It is a manually operated fitting that does not require any maintenance. However, there
          are a few things you can do to keep your Turnplus in good working condition:
        </p>

        <ul>
          <li>
            Inspect the mechanism regularly. Look for any signs of wear and tear, such as loose bolts or damaged components.
            If you notice any problems, have them repaired by a qualified technician.
          </li>
          <li>Keep the mechanism clean. Wipe it down with a damp cloth after each use to remove dirt and debris.</li>
          <li>Lubricate the mechanism. Use a light lubricant, such as WD-40, to keep the moving parts working smoothly.</li>
          <li>Store the mechanism properly. When you are not using the Turnplus, store it in a dry, cool place.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          By following these simple maintenance tips, you can help ensure that your Turnplus swivel seat mechanism will last
          for many years to come.
        </p>

        <p>Here are some additional tips for maintaining your Turnplus swivel seat mechanism:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>If you live in a coastal or cold region, you may need to lubricate the mechanism more frequently.</li>
          <li>If you use the Turnplus frequently, you may need to replace the lubricant every year or two.</li>
          <li>If you are ever unsure about how to maintain your Turnplus, consult the manufacturer’s instructions.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          The Turnplus swivel seat is a valuable tool for people with disabilities. By following these simple maintenance
          tips, you can help keep your Turnplus in good working condition and ensure that it continues to provide you with
          years of reliable service.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="sidebar" aria-label="Products">
        <div class="products-card">
          <h2>Products</h2>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/turnplus" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="video-frame">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nlMO30_RrKc"
                title="TurnPlus video"
                loading="lazy"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">TurnPlus</p>
              <p class="product-link">Swivel solution for easier entry/exit.</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/turnplus-electric" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="video-frame">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ytQ7nRd8rf4"
                title="TurnPlus Electric video"
                loading="lazy"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">TurnPlus Electric</p>
              <p class="product-link">Powered swivel seat convenience.</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/turnplus-accelerate" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="video-frame">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-bSUnSfkD-8"
                title="TurnPlus Accelerate video"
                loading="lazy"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">TurnPlus Accelerate</p>
              <p class="product-link">Rapid, smooth swivel assistance.</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </article>

  <RelatedPosts currentSlug={currentSlug} />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .article {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .article-head h1 {
    margin: 0.35rem 0 0;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .article-date {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--secondary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .article-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .article-body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  h2 {
    color: #451e5d;
    margin: 0.35rem 0 0.15rem;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-body);
  }

  .sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
  }

  .products-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 0.9rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .products-card h2 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .product-card {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 0.6rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    background: #f9f9f9;
  }

  .product-card:hover {
    border-color: #451e5d;
  }

  .video-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #000;
  }

  .video-frame iframe {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }

  .product-body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.15rem;
  }

  .product-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .product-link {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .article-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .sidebar {
      position: static;
    }
  }
</style>
